criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — defined the valuation problem and listed knowns/unknowns and parameterized assumptions; 
Implement — built a 5-year DCF, scenarios, and sensitivity tests; 
Validate — cross-checked DCF vs trading comps and precedent transactions; 
Evolve — modeled strategic synergies and phased/probability-weighted them; 
Reflect — produced a clear bid recommendation and walk-away rule based on quantitative results and qualitative judgment.
